data.description: Don’t miss out! This spacious condo offers an unparalleled blend of comfort, style, and convenience. Tons of updates including new floors and a beautifully updated kitchen. The sizable primary bedroom features a bathroom that’s sure to impress.  Relax with your morning coffee on the private deck and enjoy the ease of an attached garage and first floor laundry room. The substantial basement is a blank slate ready for you to add your personal touch.  Newer furnace, air conditioner, and windows. This home has it all!  Book your showing today!
